HAIN%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fwhy-nep-has-revived-the-language-debate%2Farticleshow%2F118658410.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20This%20UFC%20Belt%20Found%20A%20Place%20At%20Trump-Zelensky%20Showdown%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20golden-coloured%20belt%20from%20the%20Ultimate%20Fighting%20Championship%20(UFC)%20sat%20propped%20in%20one%20corner%20of%20the%20hall%20as%20a%20shouting%20match%20ensued%20between%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20his%20Ukraine%20counterpart%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20at%20the%20White%20House%20yesterday.%20It%20came%20as%20a%20gift%20from%20Zelensky%20to%20Trump%20in%20line%20with%20souvenirs%20brought%20by%20leaders%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UFC%20belt%20was%20won%20by%20Ukrainian%20boxer%20Oleksandr%20Usyk%20last%20year%20by%20defeating%20British%20boxer%20Tyson%20Fury.%20It%20accompanied%20Zelensky%20as%20he%20entered%20the%20White%20House%20to%20discuss%20a%20ceasefire%20with%20Russia%2C%20a%20deal%20now%20in%20tatters%20after%20an%20ugly%20clash%20of%20the%20presidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20noise%20from%20their%20argument%2C%20however%2C%20overshadowed%20Ukraine's%20greatest%20sports%20prize%20given%20as%20a%20gift%20to%20Trump.%20What%20appeared%20to%20be%20a%20move%20by%20Zelensky%20to%20get%20into%20Trump's%20good%20books%20after%20being%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Bterrorist%26quot%3B%20did%20little%20in%20his%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gift%20was%20likely%20even%20ignored.%20More%20humiliation%20followed%20as%20the%20Ukrainian%20delegation%20was%20asked%20to%20leave%2C%20their%20joint%20press%20conference%20was%20cancelled%2C%20and%20a%20lavish%20lunch%20made%20for%20the%20guests%20was%20never%20served.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20at%20the%20Oval%20Office%20began%20on%20cordial%20terms%20as%20Trump%20and%20Zelensky%20prepared%20to%20sign%20a%20rare%20minerals%20deal.%20The%20two%20leaders%20shook%20hands%20and%20Trump%20even%20joked%20about%20Zelensky's%20outfit%20-%20a%20military-style%20shirt%20usually%20worn%20by%20Ukraine's%20wartime%20leaders.%20But%20the%20situation%20went%20jaw-droppingly%20wrong%20within%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZelensky%20tried%20to%20tone%20things%20down%2C%20but%20it%20exploded%20as%20Vice%20President%20JD%20Vance%20accused%20the%20Ukraine%20leader%20of%20not%20being%20%26quot%3Bthankful%26quot%3B%20for%20US%20support.%20When%20Zelensky%20questioned%20the%20calls%20for%20diplomacy%2C%20Vance%20said%20he%20was%20being%20disrespectful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20presidents%2C%20who%20knew%20how%20to%20play%20to%20the%20cameras%2C%20then%20engaged%20in%20a%20battle%20of%20words%20-%20with%20the%20former's%20suggestion%20that%20the%20US%20would%20%26quot%3Bfeel%20it%20in%20the%20future%26quot%3B%20if%20it%20doesn't%20help%20Ukraine%20infuriating%20Trump.%20The%20US%20President%20snapped%20at%20Zelensky%2C%20%26quot%3BDon't%20tell%20us%20what%20we%20are%20going%20to%20feel%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20voice%20rose%20and%20the%20political%20showman%20cautioned%20Zelensky%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bgambling%20with%20World%20War%203%26quot%3B.%20Shortly%20after%2C%20Zelensky%20left%20the%20White%20House%2C%20and%20there%20was%20no%20joint%20press%20conference.%20The%20formal%20lunch%20hosted%20by%20the%20White%20House%20for%20visiting%20leaders%20was%20also%20called%20off%2C%20but%20the%20episode%20was%20far%20from%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ugly%20exchange%20surprised%20world%20leaders.%20Canada%20and%20European%20allies%20rallied%20behind%20the%20Ukrainian%20President%20while%20Russia%20praised%20Trump's%20%26quot%3Brestraint%26quot%3B%20against%20Zelensky.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740890340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fu172fiao_trump-zelensky-ufc-belt_625x300_02_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.