dia's%20Eternal%20Wonder%20And%20Humility%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20my%20friend%20and%20video%20journalist%20Pooja%20Arya%20and%20I%20trekked%20along%20the%20Sangam%20at%20the%20Mahakumbh%20in%20Prayagraj%2C%20attempting%20to%20capture%20the%20essence%20of%20the%20largest%20gathering%20on%20Earth.%20We%20also%20interviewed%20two%20policemen%20diligently%20manning%20one%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3EKhoya-Paaya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(lost%20and%20found)%20centres.%20These%20centres%20are%20the%20most%20active%20at%20Mahakumbh%2C%20buzzing%20with%20anxious%20people%20and%20proactive%20officials%20and%20volunteers%2C%20trying%20broken%20Assamese%2C%20Telugu%2C%20and%20other%20languages%20with%20gestures%2C%20asking%20the%20lost%20person%20to%20remain%20calm%20and%20remember%20as%20much%20as%20they%20can%20about%20their%20family%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20asked%20one%20of%20the%20cops%20if%20the%20challenge%20was%20bigger%20with%20lost%20children%20or%20senior%20pilgrims%2C%20and%20he%20promptly%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3Balways%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebuzurg%20%3C%2Fem%3E(senior%20people).%20They%20are%20invariably%20from%20other%20states%2C%20and%20the%20language%20is%20difficult%20to%20understand.%20They%20are%20tense%20about%20whether%20their%20family%20members%20will%20come%20or%20not.%20When%20kids%20get%20lost%2C%20parents%20search%20frantically%20and%20eventually%20find%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBritish%20economist%20Joan%20Robinson%20once%20remarked%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20frustrating%20thing%20about%20India%20is%20that%20whatever%20you%20can%20rightly%20say%20about%20India%2C%20the%20opposite%20is%20also%20true.%26quot%3B%20This%20insight%20has%20often%20helped%20me%20understand%20the%20country%20better.%20It%20applies%20not%20only%20to%20India%20at%20different%20times%20but%20also%20to%20us%20as%20Indians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F14f5sfd_maha-kumbh-afp_625x300_02_March_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20am%20glad%20my%20country%20is%20full%20of%20paradoxes%2C%20and%20I'll%20tell%20you%20why.%20While%20the%20policeman's%20experience%20was%20significant%2C%20in%20the%20very%20same%20Mahakumbh%2C%20I%20also%20witnessed%20something%20truly%20heartwarming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20large%20family%20from%20Hubbali%20in%20Karnataka%20that%20had%20come%20to%20Mahakumbh%20with%2021%20members%2C%20after%20visiting%20Ayodhya.%20One%20of%20the%20older%20members%20had%20gone%20missing%20in%20Ayodhya%20and%20was%20found%20after%20six%20hours.%20Terrified%2C%20the%20family%20had%20made%20a%20long%20rope%20of%20at%20least%20a%20dozen%20dupattas%20that%20all%20of%20them%20would%20hold%20on%20to%20while%20walking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20oldest%20member%20is%2089%20and%20the%20youngest%20we%20have%20is%203.%20We%20will%20never%20take%20a%20risk%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20woman%20in%20the%20group%20told%20me.%20Her%20commitment%20to%20her%20family's%20safety%20was%20admirable-an%20assurance%20that%2C%20even%20in%20the%20vast%20ocean%20of%20humanity%20at%20the%20Kumbh%2C%20those%20who%20are%20lost%20eventually%20find%20their%20way%20back%20to%20their%20loved%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fover-1-3-crore-take-holy-dip-on-final-day-of-maha-kumbh-in-prayagraj-7801071%5C%22%3EOver%201.3%20Crore%20Take%20Holy%20Dip%20On%20Final%20Day%20Of%20Maha%20Kumbh%20In%20Prayagraj%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Mahakumbh%2C%20almost%20every%20pilgrim%20I%20met%20talked%20about%20a%20relative%20they%20had%20lost.%20A%20doctor%20from%20Gujarat%20even%20brought%20a%20photo%20of%20her%20deceased%20grandparents%20who%20had%20taken%20her%20to%20her%20first%20Kumbh%20several%20years%20ago.%20A%20social%20worker%20from%20Delhi%20brought%20her%2083-year-old%20father%20to%20the%20Kumbh%20in%20what%20she%20described%20as%20an%20impulsive%20decision.%20%26quot%3BI%20lost%20my%20mother%20last%20year.%20Papa%20had%20become%20quiet%20since%20then.%20He%20doesn't%20hear%20or%20speak.%20But%20we%20drove%20for%2012%20hours.%20I%20decided%20to%20do%20this%20just%20two%20days%20ago%2C%20as%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20have%20any%20regrets%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20used%20to%20grapple%20with%20questions%20about%20my%20faith%20and%20how%20it%20has%20to%20be%20projected%2C%20especially%20having%20been%20raised%20in%20a%20conservative%20household%20with%20deeply%20religious%20parents.%20Temple%20visits%20were%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20my%20life-spaces%20that%20provided%20my%20family%20with%20solace%20and%20a%20strong%20sense%20of%20cultural%20identity.%20So%2C%20if%20I%20was%20going%20to%20the%20Kumbh%2C%20there%20was%20never%20any%20doubt%20on%20whether%20I%20would%20take%20a%20dip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fs6o33uno_maha-kumbh-afp_625x300_02_March_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20female%20journalist%2C%20I%20have%20spent%20years%20traveling%20through%20villages%20and%20towns%2C%20where%20the%20people%20of%20this%20country%20have%20humbled%20me%20with%20their%20insights%20on%20politics%2C%20social%20dynamics%2C%20traditions%2C%20and%20folklore.%20Their%20knowledge%20has%20shaped%20my%20understanding%2C%20and%20yet%2C%20I%20have%20often%20never%20had%20the%20chance%20to%20thank%20them%20for%20these%20lessons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20millions%20of%20them%20go%20to%20the%20Sangam%20for%20what%20they%20believe%20in%2C%20who%20am%20I%20to%20question%20them%3F%20I%20was%20grateful%20to%20spend%20two%20days%20among%20them%2C%20listening%20to%20their%20aspirations%20and%20struggles%2C%20reflecting%20on%20how%20much%20the%20country%20has%20changed%2C%20and%20how%20much%20of%20it%20remains%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia's%20glorious%20diversity%20in%20full%20display%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20we%20were%20at%20Mahakumbh%2C%20we%20had%20no%20VIP%20access.%20I%20saw%20largely%20regulated%20crowds%2C%20with%20people%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20-%20each%20group%20distinctly%20different.%20The%20Bengalis%20and%20Gujaratis%20were%20far%20more%20organized.%20Rajasthani%20pilgrims%20arrived%20in%20buses%2C%20often%20with%20more%20women%20than%20men%2C%20who%20would%20break%20into%20delightful%20renditions%20of%20Krishna%20and%20Sudama%20songs%20and%20perform%20Ghoomar%20dances%20at%20the%20drop%20of%20a%20hat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20frequently%20encountered%20people%20from%20Bihar%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20some%20from%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20and%20large%20groups%20from%20Assam%2C%20who%20diligently%20carried%20home%20cans%20of%20Gangajal.%20The%20pontoon%20bridges%20built%20over%20the%20Ganga%2C%20along%20with%20bike%20riders%20navigating%20the%20area%2C%20made%20movement%20easier%20for%20the%20pilgrims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fiit-baba-to-kalyug-ka-shravan-8-viral-moments-from-maha-kumbh-that-took-internet-by-storm-7799718%5C%22%3E8%20Viral%20Moments%20From%20Maha%20Kumbh%20That%20Took%20Internet%20By%20Storm%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYoungsters%20discussed%20Instagram%20reels%20and%20stories%2C%20while%20others%20focused%20on%20performing%20pujas%20correctly%20without%20exceeding%20their%20budgets.%20An%20NRI%20was%20constantly%20on%20a%20video%20call%2C%20showing%20his%20children%20in%20Texas%20the%20magic%20of%20India%2C%20while%20a%20bangle%20seller%20played%20peekaboo%20with%20her%20infant%2C%20reassuring%20him%20that%20they%20would%20soon%20return%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20with%20VIP%20access%20undoubtedly%20had%20an%20easier%20time%20reaching%20well-managed%20areas.%20Across%20the%20river%20from%20Arail%20Ghat%2C%20newer%2C%20swanky%20ashrams%20had%20sprung%20up%20in%20the%20past%20ten%20months.%20I%20also%20found%20the%20police%20exceptionally%20helpful%20in%20providing%20directions%20and%20answering%20general%20queries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahashivaratri%20brought%20unprecedented%20traffic%20snarls%2C%20but%20at%20the%20ghats%2C%20the%20crowd%20remained%20well-regulated.%20The%20Mauni%20Amavasya%20stampede%2C%20which%20claimed%20over%2030%20lives%2C%20had%20taught%20the%20police%20important%20lessons%3A%20The%20dip-or%20%3Cem%3Edubki%3C%2Fem%3E-in%20the%20Sangam%20is%20the%20sole%20expectation%20of%20pilgrims.%20Ensuring%20that%20the%20bathing%20areas%20remained%20supervised%20was%20crucial.%20A%20senior%20police%20official%20explained%20that%2C%20in%20the%20past%2C%20bathing%20was%20restricted%20to%20specific%20time%20slots.%20However%2C%20this%20time%2C%20people%20were%20taking%20dips%20throughout%20the%20day%20and%20even%20at%20night.%20%26quot%3BThe%20bath%20makes%20everything%20right.%20After%20that%2C%20all%20complaints%20about%20unclean%20toilets%20or%20the%20long%20walk%20to%20the%20ghats%20are%20forgotten%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20police%20officer%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Furhlpccg_maha-kumbh-afp_625x300_02_March_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20have%20always%20believed%20that%20faith%20and%20its%20expression%20are%20deeply%20personal.%20Patriarchal%20norms%20in%20religion%20remain%20deeply%20entrenched.%20However%2C%20social%20events%20and%20gatherings%20that%20are%20inclusive%20and%20free%20from%20hierarchical%20structures%20are%20always%20a%20joy%20to%20witness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShiva%20is%20an%20all-encompassing%20deity%2C%20the%20lord%20of%20the%20masses%20who%20form%20the%20soul%20of%20this%20country.%20His%20wedding%20procession%20is%20one%20where%20everyone%20is%20invited%2C%20and%20the%20Kumbh%2C%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20mirrors%20that%20inclusivity.%20I%20have%20often%20lauded%20the%20concept%20of%20one%20well%2C%20one%20temple%2C%20one%20crematorium%20as%20a%20means%20of%20fostering%20social%20cohesion-and%20there%20is%20no%20greater%20unifying%20force%20than%20a%20river.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20engage%20in%20debates%20over%20science%20versus%20faith%20because%2C%20to%20me%2C%20society%20and%20people%20are%20greater%20forces.%20I%20do%20not%20believe%20that%20taking%20a%20dip%20in%20the%20Ganga%20at%20a%20specific%20time%20can%20wash%20away%20all%20sins.%20A%20scientific%20temper%20is%20essential%20for%20any%20society%20to%20progress%2C%20as%20are%20quality%20education%20and%20skill%20development.%20Yet%2C%20I%20was%20wrong%20to%20assume%20that%20Mahakumbh%20is%20merely%20about%20%3Cem%3Eaastha%20%3C%2Fem%3E(faith)%20and%20%3Cem%3Evyavastha%20%3C%2Fem%3E(arrangements).%20It%20is%20much%20more%20than%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaha-kumbh-of-records-this-45-day-festival-of-faith-set-multiple-guinness-world-records-7814840%5C%22%3EThis%2045-Day%20Festival%20Of%20Faith%20Has%20Set%20Multiple%20Guinness%20World%20Records%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mahakumbh%20is%20an%20ode%20to%20the%20warmth%20and%20wisdom%20of%20the%20people%20of%20this%20country%20-%20people%20who%20have%20learned%20to%20live%20with%20the%20fundamental%20fear%20of%20loss%2C%20who%20may%20not%20always%20have%20the%20right%20tools%20but%20have%20found%20ways%20to%20heal%20themselves%20from%20life's%20uncertainties.%20It%20is%20an%20ode%20to%20those%20who%20may%20remain%20bound%20by%20social%20and%20cultural%20structures%20but%20refuse%20to%20be%20diminished%20by%20them.%20Faith%20and%20belief%20serve%20as%20powerful%20anchors%20for%20such%20resilience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20an%20ode%20to%20the%20mother%20from%20Sangli%20who%20proudly%20told%20me%20that%20her%20daughter%2C%20who%20works%20in%20a%20big%20company%20in%20Pune%2C%20brought%20her%20to%20the%20Kumbh.%20To%20the%20man%20who%2C%20after%20taking%20multiple%20dips%20in%20the%20Ganga%2C%20will%20return%20to%20fighting%20his%20case%20in%20a%20lower%20court.%20To%20the%20woman%20who%20carefully%20wheeled%20her%20husband%20to%20the%20river%20between%20his%20dialysis%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20an%20ode%20to%20Indians%20who%20revere%20their%20parents%20but%20often%20struggle%20to%20express%20it%2C%20to%20those%20who%20believe%20their%20ancestors%20got%20many%20things%20right%20-%20and%20some%20things%20wrong.%20To%20the%20boatman%20who%20taught%20me%20that%20the%20Yamuna's%20waters%20are%20a%20deeper%20hue%20than%20the%20Ganga's.%20And%2C%20above%20all%2C%20to%20the%20countless%20individuals%20who%20made%20the%20Mahakumbh%20what%20it%20was-a%20celebration%20of%20the%20eternal%20wonder%20and%20humility%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Vasudha%20Venugopal%20is%20an%20Anchor%20and%20Political%20Editor%20at%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740889860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fl43bacsg_maha-kumbh-afp_625x300_02_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmahakumbh-a-celebration-of-indias-eternal-wonder-and-humility-7827819%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Mahakumbh%20is%20an%20ode%20to%20the%20warmth%20and%20wisdom%20of%20the%20people%20of%20this%20country%20-%20who%20have%20learned%20to%20live%20with%20the%20fundamental%20fear%20of%20loss%2C%20who%20may%20not%20always%20have%20the%20right%20tools%2