agement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fmicrosoft-outlook-outage-affecting-users-in-the-us-restored%2Farticleshow%2F118658186.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWoke%20Up%20To%20Mountain%20Of%20Snow%26quot%3B%3A%20Uttarakhand%20Avalanche%20Survivor%20Recalls%20Horror%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGopal%20Joshi%2C%20one%20of%2055%20construction%20workers%20housed%20in%20containers%20near%20Mana%2C%20came%20out%20expecting%20a%20morning%20sheathed%20in%20silence%20like%20every%20day.%20What%20he%20met%20with%20was%20a%20roaring%20cascade%20of%20snow%20coming%20right%20at%20them%20with%20a%20ferocious%20speed.%20The%20avalanche%2C%20common%20in%20winter%20in%20the%20area%2C%20eventually%20left%20the%20site%20in%20a%20state%20of%20ruin%2C%20and%20the%20workers%20plodding%20in%20thick%20snow%20to%20outrun%20a%20veritable%20entombment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFifty%20workers%20were%20rescued%2C%20while%20four%20of%20them%20died%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoshi%2C%20a%20native%20of%20Narayanbagar%20in%20Chamoli%20district%2C%20had%20been%20operating%20an%20accelerator%20machine%20for%20the%20last%20several%20months.%20The%20group%20was%20employed%20at%20a%20BRO%20camp%20by%20Vijay%20Infra%20Construction%20Company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20happened%20in%20a%20jiffy%2C%20Joshi%2C%20who%20was%20admitted%20for%20treatment%20along%20with%20his%2022%20colleagues%20in%20the%20Army's%20Jyotirmath%20hospital%2C%20recalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20weather%20was%20as%20bad%20as%20it%20had%20been%20for%20the%20last%20few%20days%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSnow%20was%20falling%20outside.%20The%20incident%20must%20have%20happened%20around%206%20am.%20As%20soon%20as%20we%20came%20out%20of%20the%20container%2C%20we%20heard%20a%20loud%20thunder.%20When%20we%20looked%20towards%20the%20top%2C%20we%20saw%20a%20deluge%20of%20snow%20rolling%20towards%20us.%20I%20shouted%20to%20alert%20my%20companions%20and%20ran.%20There%20was%20already%20several%20feet%20of%20snow%20due%20to%20which%20we%20could%20not%20run%20fast.%20After%20two%20hours%2C%20the%20soldiers%20of%20the%20Indo-Tibetan%20Border%20Police%20came%20to%20rescue%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoshi%20and%20his%20companions%20were%20brought%20from%20Mana%20to%20Jyotirmath%20on%20Saturday%20by%20army%20helicopters%20for%20treatment%20at%20an%20army%20hospital.%20He%20bore%20a%20minor%20injury%20on%20his%20head%20and%20pain%20in%20chest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVipin%20Kumar%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20who%20hurt%20his%20back%2C%20said%20he%20was%20buried%20in%20snow%20for%20about%2015%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20able%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20snow%20only%20when%20the%20avalanche%20stopped%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kumar%2C%20who%20said%20it%20was%20his%20second%20birth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20worker%2C%20Manoj%20Bhandari%2C%20said%20he%20woke%20up%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bmountain%20of%20snow%26quot%3B%20sliding%20from%20the%20peak.%20%26quot%3BI%20shouted%20to%20alert%20everyone%20and%20ran%20behind%20the%20loader%20machine%20parked%20nearby%20to%20save%20myself.%20Three%20workers%20from%20Mathura%20said%20their%20bid%20to%20escape%20the%20avalanche%20was%20hindered%20by%20%26quot%3Bseveral%20feet%20of%20snow.%26quot%3B%20Jagbir%20Singh%20of%20Amritsar%2C%20Punjab%2C%20said%20he%20and%20his%20companions%20ran%20towards%20Badrinath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%2019%20people%20who%20were%20rescued%20and%20brought%20to%20the%20Army%20Hospital%20here%20had%20injuries%20on%20their%20back%2C%20head%2C%20hands%2C%20and%20legs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20them%20who%20suffered%20serious%20wounds%20were%20sent%20to%20AIIMS%2C%20Rishikesh%2C%20by%20a%20helicopter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20workers%20said%20they%20were%20living%20in%20five%20containers%20set%20up%20by%20a%20roadside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5