oon%20along%20the%20way.%20It%20shared%20a%20ride%20with%20a%20Japanese%20company's%20lander%20set%20to%20attempt%20a%20landing%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBlue%20Ghost%20carries%20ten%20instruments%2C%20including%20a%20lunar%20soil%20analyzer%2C%20a%20radiation-tolerant%20computer%20and%20an%20experiment%20testing%20the%20feasibility%20of%20using%20the%20existing%20global%20satellite%20navigation%20system%20to%20navigate%20the%20Moon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDesigned%20to%20operate%20for%20a%20full%20lunar%20day%20(14%20Earth%20days)%2C%20Blue%20Ghost%20is%20expected%20to%20capture%20high-definition%20imagery%20of%20a%20total%20eclipse%20on%20March%2014%2C%20when%20Earth%20blocks%20the%20Sun%20from%20the%20Moon's%20horizon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2016%2C%20it%20will%20record%20a%20lunar%20sunset%2C%20offering%20insights%20into%20how%20dust%20levitates%20above%20the%20surface%20under%20solar%20influence%20--%20creating%20the%20mysterious%20lunar%20horizon%20glow%20first%20documented%20by%20Apollo%20astronaut%20Eugene%20Cernan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHopping%20drone%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBlue%20Ghost's%20arrival%20will%20be%20followed%20on%20March%206%20by%20Intuitive%20Machines'%20IM-2%20mission%2C%20featuring%20its%20lander%20Athena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202024%2C%20Intuitive%20Machines%20became%20the%20first%20private%20company%20to%20achieve%20a%20soft%20lunar%20landing%20--%20also%20the%20first%20US%20landing%20since%20the%20crewed%20Apollo%2017%20mission%20of%201972.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20success%20was%20tempered%20by%20a%20mishap%3A%20the%20lander%20came%20down%20too%20fast%2C%20tipped%20over%20on%20impact%2C%20leaving%20it%20unable%20to%20generate%20enough%20solar%20power%20and%20cutting%20the%20mission%20short.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20the%20company%20says%20it%20has%20made%20key%20improvements%20to%20the%20hexagonal-shaped%20lander%2C%20which%20has%20a%20taller%2C%20slimmer%20profile%20than%20Blue%20Ghost%2C%20and%20is%20around%20the%20height%20of%20an%20adult%20giraffe.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAthena%20launched%20on%20Wednesday%20aboard%20a%20SpaceX%20rocket%2C%20taking%20a%20more%20direct%20route%20toward%20Mons%20Mouton%20--%20the%20southernmost%20lunar%20landing%20site%20ever%20attempted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20payloads%20include%20three%20rovers%2C%20a%20drill%20to%20search%20for%20ice%20and%20the%20star%20of%20the%20show%3A%20a%20first-of-its-kind%20hopping%20drone%20designed%20to%20explore%20the%20Moon's%20rugged%20terrain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ENASA's%20private%20Moon%20fleet%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELanding%20on%20the%20Moon%20presents%20unique%20challenges%20due%20to%20the%20absence%20of%20an%20atmosphere%2C%20making%20parachutes%20ineffective.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20spacecraft%20must%20rely%20on%20precisely%20controlled%20thruster%20burns%20to%20slow%20their%20descent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%20Intuitive%20Machines'%20first%20successful%20mission%2C%20only%20five%20national%20space%20agencies%20had%20accomplished%20this%20feat%3A%20the%20Soviet%20Union%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20China%2C%20India%20and%20Japan%2C%20in%20that%20order.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20United%20States%20is%20working%20to%20make%20private%20lunar%20missions%20routine%20through%20NASA's%20%242.6%20billion%20Commercial%20Lunar%20Payload%20Services%20(CLPS)%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20missions%20come%20at%20a%20delicate%20moment%20for%20NASA%2C%20amid%20speculation%20that%20it%20may%20scale%20back%20or%20even%20cancel%20its%20Artemis%20lunar%20program%20in%20favor%20of%20prioritizing%20Mars%20exploration%20--%20a%20key%20goal%20of%20both%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20his%20close%20advisor%2C%20SpaceX%20founder%20Elon%20Musk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20sy