e%20for%20Ukraine%2C%20protect%20European%20security%2C%20and%20secure%20our%20collective%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20earlier%2C%20Ukraine%20and%20the%20UK%20unveiled%20a%20%242.84%20billion%20loan%20agreement%20to%20support%20Ukraine's%20defence%20capabilities%2C%20to%20be%20paid%20back%20with%20the%20profits%20of%20immobilised%20sovereign%20Russian%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20funds%20will%20be%20directed%20toward%20weapons%20production%20in%20Ukraine%2C%26quot%3B%20Zelensky%20said%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20true%20justice%20--%20the%20one%20who%20started%20the%20war%20must%20be%20the%20one%20to%20pay.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESupporters%20cheered%20as%20Zelensky's%20convoy%20swept%20into%20Downing%20Street%2C%20where%20he%20was%20embraced%20by%20Starmer%20and%20posed%20for%20photographs%20before%20heading%20inside%20the%20British%20leader's%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20very%2C%20very%20welcome%20here%20in%20Downing%20Street%2C%26quot%3B%20Starmer%20told%20Zelensky.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20thank%20you%2C%20the%20people%20of%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20for%20such%20big%20support%20from%20the%20very%20beginning%20of%20this%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20Zelensky%20responded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20due%20to%20meet%20King%20Charles%20III%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leaders%20met%20behind%20closed%20doors%20for%20around%2075%20minutes%2C%20and%20embraced%20again%20as%20Starmer%20escorted%20Zelensky%20to%20his%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'A%20new%20age%20of%20infamy'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20Saturday%2C%20Zelensky%20had%20stressed%20that%20Trump's%20support%20was%20still%20%26quot%3Bcrucial%26quot%3B%20for%20Ukraine%20despite%20their%20row%20the%20previous%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20clash%20was%20a%20further%20shock%20to%20Kyiv's%20European%20allies%2C%20still%20adjusting%20to%20Washington's%20new%20stance%20on%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%20as%20cameras%20in%20the%20Oval%20Office%20rolled%2C%20Trump%20berated%20Zelensky%20for%20not%20being%20%26quot%3Bready%26quot%3B%20for%20peace%20with%20Russia%2C%20triggering%20alarm%20across%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYesterday%20evening%20underlined%20that%20a%20new%20age%20of%20infamy%20has%20begun%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Germany's%20Foreign%20Minister%20Annalena%20Baerbock.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarmer%2C%20Polish%20Prime%20Minister%20Donald%20Tusk%20and%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20were%20among%20several%20other%20European%20leaders%20who%20reiterated%20their%20support%20for%20Kyiv%20after%20the%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20the%20BBC%2C%20NATO%20chief%20Mark%20Rutte%20said%20he%20had%20told%20Zelensky%20he%20had%20to%20%26quot%3Bfind%20a%20way%26quot%3B%20to%20restore%20his%20relationship%20with%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussian%20politicians%20were%20delighted%2C%20however.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia's%20former%20president%20Dmitry%20Medvedev%20called%20Zelensky%20an%20%26quot%3Binsolent%20pig%26quot%3B%20who%20had%20received%20%26quot%3Ba%20proper%20slap%20down%20in%20the%20Oval%20Office%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Zelensky%20left%20the%20White%20House%20without%20having%20signed%20the%20deal%20on%20Kyiv's%20rare%20minerals%2C%20he%20insisted%20he%20was%20still%20ready%20to%20sign%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20first%20step%20toward%20security%20guarantees%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20crucial%20for%20us%20to%20have%20President%20Trump's%20support.%20He%20wants%20to%20end%20the%20war%2C%20but%20no%20one%20wants%20peace%20more%20than%20we%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Zelensky%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZelensky%20will%20be%20at%20Sunday's%20emergency%20talks%20in%20London%20with%20Kyiv's%20European%20backers%20--%20a%20meeting%20that%20will%20also%20be%20attended%20by%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau.