0and%20a%20message%20to%20Mr%20Zelensky%20and%20Ukraine%20that%20they%20will%20not%20stand%20alone.%20The%20strategy%20of%20President%20Trump%20and%20his%20team%20is%20still%20not%20clear%20to%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Commissioner%20said%20the%20EU%20had%20started%20getting%20strange%20messages%20during%20the%20Munich%20conference%2C%20when%20US%20Vice%20President%20JD%20Vance%20had%20been%20critical%20of%20the%20Union%20on%20several%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmphasising%20that%20everyone%20in%20the%20European%20Union%20is%20standing%20for%20peace%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20he%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3BUkrainians%20really%20deserve%20peace%20and%20they%20are%20the%20ones%20with%20the%20strongest%20wish%20to%20have%20peace.%20But%20a%20just%20peace%20can%20only%20be%20achieved%20through%20a%20formula%20of%20peace%20through%20strength.%20That%20formula%20was%20repeated%20also%20by%20Americans%20till%20now.%20This%20means%20that%20we%20need%20to%20bring%20strength%20to%20the%20Ukranians%20-%20military%2C%20financial%20and%20so%20on%20-%20to%20show%20Vladimir%20Putin%20that%20he%20will%20not%20achieve%20anything%20in%20Ukraine.%20Mr%20Putin%20started%20the%20war%2C%20he%20started%20the%20aggression.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kubilius%20also%20said%20that%20the%20United%20States%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Bwrong%20understanding%26quot%3B%20that%20their%20support%20to%20Ukraine%20was%20as%20high%20as%20the%20EU's.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20supporting%20and%20the%20Americans%20were%20supporting%20Ukraine%20quite%20a%20lot...%20but%20the%20Union's%20general%2C%20military%20and%20financial%20support%20was%20around%2030%25%20bigger%20than%20American%20support.%20Our%20support%20was%20%24130%20billion%2C%20and%20the%20US'%20was%20%24100%20billion%2C%20not%20500%20or%20whatever%20we%20hear%20from%20President%20Trump%20sometimes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Commissioner%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20military%20support%20by%20the%20US%20and%20the%20EU%20per%20year%20was%20below%200.1%25%20of%20the%20GDP%20and%20it%20can%2C%20thus%2C%20be%20increased.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20warned%20that%20not%20supporting%20Ukraine%20would%20send%20a%20signal%20to%20China%20that%20it%20can%20also%20behave%20aggressively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20we%20need%20to%20increase%20because%20Ukraine%20is%20defending%20all%20of%20us.%20It%20definitely%20defends%20us%20Europeans%20and%2C%20in%20some%20way%2C%20also%20the%20US.%20Because%20if%20the%20West%20will%20fail%20in%20Ukraine%20and%20Russia%2C%20with%20its%20aggressive%20policies%2C%20will%20win%2C%20we%20can%20see%20very%20clearly%20what%20will%20be%20the%20international%20consequences.%20I%20am%20absolutely%20sure%2C%20for%20example%2C%20China%20is%20watching%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20Ukraine.%20And%20if%20China%20will%20make%20a%20conclusion%20that%20the%20West%20is%20weak%20politically%20and%20is%20unable%20to%20stop%20Russia%20aggression%2C%20it%20can%20also%20behave%20in%20an%20aggressive%20way%2C%20either%20towards%20Taiwan%2C%20or%20whatever%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERules-Based%20Order%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20how%20India%20and%20the%20European%20Union%20can%20collaborate%20and%20ensure%20that%20the%20international%20rules-based%20order%20is%20maintained%2C%20the%20Commissioner%20said%20Europe%20is%20facing%20big%20threats%20from%20Russia%20and%20European%20intelligence%20agencies%20have%20said%20that%20Moscow%20could%20turn%20its%20aggression%20towards%20EU%20or%20NATO%20member%20states%20next.%20India%2C%20he%20pointed%20out%2C%20is%20facing%20its%20own%20threats%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20my%20view%2C%20countries%20which%20are%20based%20on%20the%20same%20principles%20of%20democracy%2C%20of%20rule%20of%20law%2C%20and%20(support%20for%20an)%20international%20order%20based%20on%20clear%20principles%20of%20sovereignty%20and%20non-aggression%20should%20unite%20and%20be%20much%20more%20proactive%20in%20not%20allowing%20countries%2C%20usually%20authoritarian%20countries%2C%20testing%20us%20with%20any%20kind%20of%20aggression%20or%20some%20kind%20of%20authoritarian%20aggressive%20axis.%20Especially%2C%20you%20know%2C%20when%20we%20are%20concerned%20about%20Russian%20behavior%2C%20we%20see%20Russia%2C%20Iran%2C%20North%20Korea%20and%20China%20somewhere%2C%20you%20know%2C%20not%20far%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20that%20is%20why%20we%20need%20to%20be%20very%20clear%20that%20we%20cannot%20allow%20anybody%20to%20behave%20in%20an%20aggressive%20way%2C%20not%20stopped%20by%20the%20international%20democratic%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'India's%20Century'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kubilius%20said%20this%20is%20the%20first%20visit%20to%20India%20by%20the%20entire%20EU%20College%20of%20Commissioners%20which%20underlines%20how%20significant%20it%20considers%20its%20strategic%20relationship%20with%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20repeating%20that%20the%2021st%20century%20will%20be%2C%20first%20of%20all%2C%20the%20century%20of%20space%20and%20the%20century%20of%20India...%20because%20of%20Indian%20development%2C%20significance%20and%20the%20geopolitical%20and%20economic%20roles%20India%20is%20playing%20and%20will%20play%20until%20the%20end%20of%20the%20century.%20The%20European%20Union%20and%20India%20are%20living%20with%20the%20same%20values%20of%20democracy%2C%20of%20human%20rights...%20and%20that%20makes%20our%20cooperation%2C%20our%20strategic%20partnership%20very%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Commissioner%20said%20he%20had%20important%20meetings%20with%20the%20Minister%20of%20Atomic%20Energy%20and%20Space%20Jitendra%20Singh%2C%20ISRO%20officials%20and%20others%20and%20that%20he%20agrees%20with%20EU%20chief%20Ursula%20von%20der%20Leyen%20that%20this%20is%20%26quot%3Bno%20time%20to%20put%20any%20kind%20of%20limits%20in%20our%20future%20cooperation%20between%20European%20Union%20and%20India%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20possibilities%20which%20we%20discussed.%20For%20example%2C%20we%20agreed%20to%20have%20a%20high-level%20strategic%20space%20dialogue%2C%20that%20our%20talks%20for%20a%20free%20trade%20agreement%20should%20be%20finished%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible...%20at%20least%20until%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year.%20Another%20point%2C%20very%20important%2C%20related%20to%20defence%20and%20security%3A%20The%20Commission%20president%20offered%20for%20us%20(EU%20and%20India)%20to%20develop%20the%20so-called%20strategic%20pact%20on%20defence%20and%20security%2C%20like%20the%20European%20Union%20has%2C%20for%20example%2C%20with%20Japan%20and%20South%20Korea%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20India%20is%20playing%20a%20very%20important%20role%20globally%20and%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region%2C%20which%20is%20also%20very%20important%20for%20the%20EU.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pact%20on%20defence%2C%20Mr%20Kubilius%20said%2C%20could%20include%20organising%20joint%20exercises%2C%20sharing%20data%20and%20space%20activities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpace%2C%20Defence%20Cooperation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStressing%20that%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bvery%20impressed%26quot%3B%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20ambitious%20space%20programme%2C%20the%20Commissioner%20said%20he%20had%20discussed%20India's%20plans%20to%20achieve%20a%20crewed%20moon%20landing%20by%202040%2C%20building%20a%20space%20station%20and%20the%20recent%20successful%20docking%20experiment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can%20expect%20that%20there%20will%20be%20some%20kind%20of%20manufacturing%20in%20space.%20We%20can%20expect%20that%20there%20will%20be%20energy%20production%20in%20space.%20And%20everything%20that%20will%20open%20new%20possibilities%20for%20cooperation%2C%20for%20joint%20projects%20(between%20the%20EU%20and%20India)...%20If%20you%20are%20able%20to%20show%20that%20in%20space%20you%20are%20able%20to%20do%20something%20significant%2C%20it%20means%20that%20you%20are%20really%20good%20and%20strong%20partners%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20EU%20companies%20would%20partner%20with%20Indian%20firms%20and%20establish%20joint%20manufacturing%20in%20India%2C%20Mr%20Kubilius%20pointed%20again%20to%20Ms%20von%20der%20Leyen's%20%26quot%3Bno-limit%26quot%3B%20partnership%20comment%20and%20said%20he%20could%20not%20see%20why%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20stressed%20that%2C%20given%20Russia's%20%26quot%3Baggression%26quot%3B%2C%20India%20could%20be%20a%20good%20option%20to%20help%20fill%20the%20gaps%20in%20the%20EU's%20defence%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20that%20way%2C%20really%2C%20we%20need%20to%20look%20also%20at%20how%20those%20gaps%20should%20be%20filled%20by%20whatever%20means%20we%20can%20implement%2C%20including%2C%20for%20example%2C%20joint%20ventures%2C%20joint%20projects.%20India%20has%20a%20really%20very%20well-known%20defence%20industry.%20You%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20skilled%20people.%20The%20production%20cost%20in%20India%20is%20lower%20than%20it%20is%20in%20Europe.%20So%2C%20why%20not%20look%20for%20beneficial%20cooperation%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740850260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fvsetjpvg_andrius-kubilius_625x300_01_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fandrius-kubilius-european-union-india-donald-trump-zelensky-not-backing-ukraine-will-tell-china-it-can-behave-aggressively-eu-commissioner-7825272%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Speaking%20out%20on%20the%20spat%20between%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20his%20Ukrainian%20counterpart%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%2C%20European%20Union%20Commissioner%20