20made%20holding%20cash%20slightly%20less%20attractive.%20The%20hope%20was%20that%20as%20yields%20on%20safer%20assets%20came%20down%2C%20investors%20would%20flock%20back%20to%20the%20stock%20market%20and%20spur%20a%20fresh%20run%20of%20gains.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20the%20bulls%20are%20counting%20on%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-money-wall-drive-stocks-july-record-highs-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20%26quot%3Bwall%20of%20money%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20rescue%20the%20stock%20market%20during%20its%20next%20big%20sell-off%2C%20they%20might%20adjust%20their%20thinking.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20why.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d721a21d-48ca-4702-8b2b-3a6733a38fbb%5C%22%3EIt's%20cash%20optimization%2C%20not%20risk%20reduction%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20with%20this%20bif%20the%20bull%20thesis%20is%20that%20much%20of%20the%20increase%20in%20assets%20in%20money%20market%20funds%20is%20being%20driven%20by%20cash%20optimization%20decisions%20among%20investors%2C%20according%20to%20Jay%20Hatfield%2C%20CEO%20of%20Infrastructure%20Capital%20Advisors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20period%20of%20rising%20money%20market%20assets%2C%20the%20level%20of%20M1%2C%20which%20included%20checking%20accounts%20but%20not%20money%20market%20assets%2C%20declined%20by%20over%20%242%20trillion%2C%20indicating%20that%20the%20increase%20in%20money%20market%20balances%20was%20mostly%20optimization%20activity%20and%20not%20risk%20reduction%20activity%2C%26quot%3B%20Hatfield%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20investors%20took%20advantage%20of%205%25%20cash%20yields%20by%20transferring%20their%20money%20out%20of%20low-yielding%20bank%20checking%20accounts%20and%20transferring%20it%20into%20money%20market%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20long%20as%20cash%20yields%20don't%20crash%20to%20zero%2C%20it's%20unlikely%20that%20cash%20on%20the%20sidelines%20will%20seek%20other%20investment%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20even%20if%20yields%20did%20tumble%20to%200%25%2C%20that%20probably%20means%20the%20economy%20is%20in%20trouble%2C%20in%20which%20case%20investors%20will%20probably%20not%20be%20eager%20to%20move%20their%20risk-free%20cash%20into%20a%20more%20volatile%20asset%20like%20stocks.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226664664e-a014-43c1-a343-1375b9d3fe94%5C%22%3E%247%20trillion%20ain't%20what%20it%20used%20to%20be%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Larry%20Tentarelli%2C%20chief%20technical%20strategist%20at%20the%20Blue%20Chip%20Daily%20Trend%20Report%2C%20the%20record%20%247%20trillion%20in%20cash%20isn't%20all%20that%20impressive%20an%20amount%2C%20at%20least%20on%20a%20relative%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20data%20analysis%20by%20Tentarelli%20showed%20that%20money%20market%20cash%20has%20been%20steadily%20declining%20as%20a%20percentage%20of%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500's%20total%20market%20capitalization%20even%20as%20the%20absolute%20number%20has%20hit%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20point%20is%20ultimately%20noise%20for%20Tentarelli%2C%20who%20thinks%20it%20should%20be%20ignored.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20that%20we%20should%20expect%20a%20sudden%20influx%20of%20cash%20into%20the%20equity%20markets%20from%20money%20market%20funds%20or%20that%20this%20'dry%20powder'%20should%20be%20considered%20as%20either%20bullish%20(money%20ready%20to%20come%20in)%20or%20bearish%20(investors%20scared%20to%20commit)%2C%26quot%3B%20Tentarelli%20said%20in%20an%20email%20to%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e08be2b1-6a3e-4c27-8c35-b9f5a4fdcb56%5C%22%3EStrategic%20cash%20reserves%20do%20exist%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20some%20investors%20sitting%20on%20cash%20are%20waiting%20to%20pounce%20on%20any%20significant%20stock%20market%20decline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBen%20Hunt%2C%20a%20retail%20investor%20from%20Kentucky%2C%20told%20BI%20earlier%20this%20month%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretail-investors-stock-market-bullish-sentiment-trump-trade-hood-pltr-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20viewed%20the%20stock%20market%20as%20ripe%20for%20a%20correction%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20believed%20investors%20were%20exhibiting%20signs%20of%20exuberance.%20This%20key%20behavior%20has%20historically%20occurred%20right%20before%20a%20market%20peak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20plan%20to%20raise%20up%20to%2050%25%20cash%20in%20my%20portfolio%20before%20the%20end%20of%20the%20quarter%2C%26quot%3B%20Hunt%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20was%20already%20at%2030%25%20cash%20in%20his%20portfolio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHunt%20said%20he%20would%20use%20that%20cash%20to%20strategically%20buy%20a%20bigger%20decline%20in%20the%20stock%20market%2C%20%26quot%3Bhopefully%20at%20lower%20prices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20any%20case%2C%20dip%20buyers%20don't%20seem%20to%20see%20any%20bargains%20just%20yet%20as%20the%20stock%20market%20declines%20on%20worries%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-today-dow-worst-day-economic-data-consumer-sentiment-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efading%20economic%20growth.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fs%26amp%3Bp_500%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ES%26amp%3BP%20500%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fnasdaq_100%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENasdaq%20100%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20down%204.5%25%20and%207.5%25%20since%20their%20peaks%20in%20mid-February%20and%20have%20yet%20to%20stage%20any%20significant%20bounceback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-7-trillion-cash-bull-case-money-market-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740834001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66be61391aa2ac29ee31aed7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-7-trillion-cash-bull-case-money-market-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Money%20market%20cash%20has%20been%20steadily%20declining%20as%20a%20percentage%20of%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500's%20total%20market%20capitalization%20even%20as%20the%20absolute%20number%20hits%20records.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mfox%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Fox)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A27%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-outlook-7-trillion-cash-bull-case-money-market-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20cofounder%20shares%20how%20he%20pitched%20his%20startup%20and%20'earned'%20his%20way%20to%20compete%20with%20Microsoft%20and%20Salesforce%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Taylor%20Francis%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c1f9d9b1834fe31165cfb6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETaylor%20Francis%2C%20cofounder%20of%20Watershed%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20his%20startup%20serves%2060%20of%20the%20Fortune%20500%20companies.%3Cp%3EWatershed%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETaylor%20Francis%20cofounded%20a%20carbon-emissions%20data-tracking%20startup%20in%202019.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20startup%20said%20it%20raised%20%24100M%20in%20a%20Series%20C%20funding%20round%20in%202024%20at%20a%20%241.8B%20valuation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20shared%20how%20he%20pitched%20his%20climate-change-focused%20startup%20to%20investors%20during%20Trump's%20first%20term.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20cofounder%20of%20Watershed%2C%20an%20emissions%20data-tracking%20startup%2C%20Taylor%20Francis's%20job%20is%20to%20convince%20companies%20to%20spend%20money%20on%20reducing%20their%20carbon%20footprint%20%E2%80%94%20even%20in%20a%20political%20landscape%20that%20may%20be%20hostile%20to%20climate%20initiatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrancis%20co-founded%20the%20software%20startup%20in%202019%20with%20two%20former%20Stripe%20colleagues%2C%20Avi%20Itskovich%20and%20Christian%20Anderson%2C%20at%20the%20tail%20end%20of%20the%20first%20Trump%20administration%2C%20which%20aggressively%20scaled%20back%20climate-oriented%20incentives%20and%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20their%20investor%20pitch%20was%20simple%3A%20There's%20money%20to%20be%20made%20in%20climate%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESix%20years%20later%2C%20with%20the%20onset%20of%20a%20second%20Trump%20term%2C%20Francis%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20message%20remains%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20been%20here%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202024%2C%20the%20startup%20announced%20a%20%24100%20million%20Series%20C%20funding%20round%20at%20a%20%241.8%20billion%20valuation.%20And%20January%202025%20was%20Watershed's%20%26quot%3Bbest%20month%20ever%20as%20a%20business%26quot%3B%20regarding%20new%20revenue%2C%20Francis%20said.%20He%20did%20not%20disclose%20a%20figure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Francis%20said%20his%20biggest%20competitors%20are%20Salesforce%20and%20Microsoft%20which%20also%20offer%20similar%20emissions-tracking%20services.%20He%20said%20his%20clients%20include%2060%20of%20the%20Fortune%20500%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20like%20that's%20a%20problem%20we've%20earned%20our%20way%20into%20recently%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20visited%20Francis%20at%20Watershed's%2023%2C000-square-foot%20office%20in%20San%20Francisco's%20SoMa%20neighborhood%2C%20where%20his%20nearly%20400%20employees%20are%20encouraged%20to%20come%20into%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20BI%20he%20likes%20to%20operate%20in%20an%20%26quot%3Bold%20school%26quot%3B%20way%3A%20in%20person%2C%20where%20people%20can%20freely%20exchange%20ideas%20in%20front%20of%20a%20whiteboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrancis%20shared%20how%20he%20first%20pitched%20his%20company%20to%20investors%20in%202019%20and%20the%20challenges%20he%20navigates%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20interview%20was%20condensed%20and%20edited%20for%20clarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWas%20it%20hard%20getting%20companies%20onboard%20with%20Watershed%20in%202019%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYeah%2C%20I%20mean%2C%202019%20was%20in%20the%20first%20Trump%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20seemed%20no%20one%20had%20ever%20done%20this%20before%20%E2%80%94%20getting%20companies%20to%20spend%20money%20on%20software%20for%20climate.%20People%20had%20spent%20money%20on%20consultants%2C%20they'd%20spent%20money%20on%20%5Bcarbon%5D%20offsets.%20And%20I%20think%20that%20the%20mega%20trend%20that%20we%20are%20both%20riding%20and%20trying%20to%20accelerate%20is%20that%20climate%20is%20getting%20more%20and%20more%20in-the-money%20for%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThat%20was%20the%20pitch%20at%20the%20time%20%E2%80%94%20there's%20money%20in%20pursuing%20climate%20initiatives.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHonestly%2C%20the%20first%20slide%20of%20our%20sales%20deck%20was%20the%20same%20in%202019%20as%20it%20is%20today.%20Literally%20the%20first%20slide%20of%20the%20sales%20deck.%20It%20looks%20better%2C%20it's%20been%20redesigned%2C%20but%20it%20still%20says%3A%20%26quot%3BSoftware%20to%20measure%2C%20reduce%2C%20and%20report%20your%20carbon%20emissions%2C%20because%20climate%20action%20is%20good%20for%20your%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20the%20thing%2C%20I'll%20say%20January%202025%20was%20our%20best%20month%20ever%20as%20a%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20do%20you%20think%20is%20happening%20there%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20that%20we%20are%20indexed%20to%20companies%20doing%20the%20work%20on%20climate%2C%20not%20indexed%20to%20companies%20talking%20publicly%20about%20their%20work%20on%20climate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20see%20now%20that%20companies%20are%20behind%20the%20scenes.%20When%20you're%20an%20enterprise%20software%2C%20you%20kind%20of%20get%20to%20see%20the%20inside%20of%20organizations%20and%20whether%20they're%20thinking%20about%20this%20in%20a%20thoughtful%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20companies%20are%20going%20about%20this%20with%20more%20organizational%20seriousness%20now%20than%20they%20did%20three%20years%20ago.%20They're%20saying%20much%20less%20about%20it%2C%20but%20the%20executive%20leader%20who's%20responsible%20has%20shifted%20from%20chief%20sustainability%20officer%20to%20the%20chief%20financial%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Watershed%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c1319f69253ccddf97de78%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWatershed%20office%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20California.%3Cp%3ELloyd%20Lee%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20are%20your%20competitors%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20and%20Salesforce.%20They%20have%20these%20modules.%20It's%20nice%20market%20validation%20that%20they%20think%20this%20is%20a%20big%20opportunity%2C%20but%20there's%20just%20a%20difference%20in%20product%20quality%20when%20it's%20the%20only%20thing%20you%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA%20Salesforce%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20email%20that%20sustainability%20management%20is%20%26quot%3Bfundamentally%20a%20data%20challenge%26quot%3B%20that%20requires%20a%20unified%20platform.%20A%20Microsoft%20spokesperson%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20the%20hardest%20thing%20right%20now%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHonestly%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20pretty%20pedestrian%3A%20enterprise%20software%20challenges.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EHow%20do%20you%20make%20it%20a%20no-brainer%20for%20companies%20to%20buy%20a%20nice%20piece%2