0to%20their%20guests.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20found%20a%20local%20sugarcane%20juice%20vendor%20and%20asked%20for%20special%20permission%20from%20the%20church%20to%20bring%20him%20inside%20the%20church%20quadrangle%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Svetlana.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20leftover%20sugarcane%20pulp%20was%20used%20to%20feed%20cows.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESorting%20and%20eliminating%20waste%20at%20the%20venue%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20also%20thought%20about%20waste%20management%20during%20the%20event.%20The%20bride%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20a%20waste%20management%20team%20on-site%20to%20ensure%20that%20everything%20was%20sorted%20and%20managed%20properly.%20We%20set%20up%20colour-coded%20bamboo%20bins%20for%20recycling%20and%20composting%20throughout%20the%20venue.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20dustbins%20were%20filled%2C%20the%20waste%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20back%20end%2C%20where%20a%20team%20of%20waste%20workers%20carefully%20opened%20each%20bag%20and%20sorted%20the%20waste%20into%20nine%20different%20categories.%20We%20kept%20paper%20separate%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F228658%2Fhow-to-garden-organic-fertiliser-fruit-peels-banana-skin-onion-orange-mango-how-to-do-diy-tips-tan42%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efood%20scraps%20in%20another%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20coconuts%20in%20yet%20another.%20The%20food%20scraps%20and%20coconuts%20were%20sent%20off%20for%20composting.%20We%20also%20made%20sure%20to%20separate%20organic%20waste%20from%20recyclable%20materials.%20All%20paper%20and%20cardboard%20were%20sent%20for%20recycling.%20Nothing%20went%20to%20the%20landfill%2C%20everything%20was%20reused%2C%20repurposed%2C%20or%20recycled%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Joel%2C%20his%20voice%20filled%20with%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20even%20had%20something%20in%20place%20for%20our%20smoker%20friends.%20To%20prev