SK-4%20turmeric%20variety%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20trials%20were%20spread%20over%20two%20years%20and%20we%20found%20that%20SK-4%20was%20characterised%20by%20its%20high%20yield%20potential%2C%20like%20Rajendra%20Sona.%20The%20latter%E2%80%99s%20seed%20material%20is%20always%20scarce%20and%20we%20hope%20the%20new%20variety%20will%20fulfil%20the%20demand.%20SK-4%20is%20a%20good%20alternative%20for%20those%20growing%20it%20in%20Konkan%E2%80%99s%20high-rainfall%20region.%20Incidentally%2C%20the%20variety%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20evaluated%20in%20low%20rainfall%20areas%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Prafulla%20Mali%2C%20horticulturist%2C%20DBSKKV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHigh%20curcumin%20content%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20variety%20possesses%20an%20attractive%20bright%20reddish-yellow%20colour%20and%20has%20big-sized%20rhizomes.%20It%20is%20a%20short%20duration%20(160-170%20days)%20variety%20suitable%20for%20high%20rainfall%20regions%20and%20with%20good%20tolerance%20to%20%3Cem%3Ekarpa%20(%3C%2Fem%3Erhizome%20rot%20disease).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20possesses%20a%20curcumin%20content%20of%204%20per%20cent.%20For%20comparison%2C%20the%20premium-yielding%20Rajapuri%20Salem%20variety%20yields%20315.29g%20fresh%20rhizome%20per%20plant%20with%20a%20curcumin%20content%20of%203.5%20per%20cent%20and%20output%20of%2032.67t%2Fha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENumerous%20farmers%20in%20Sindhudurg%20and%20Raigad%20districts%2C%20along%20with%20Ratnagiri%20are%20presently%20cultivating%20this%20variety.%20One%20Vishram%20Mali%20(58)%20of%20Velamb%20village%20in%20Guhagar%20taluka%20achieved%20the%20highest%20output%20last%20year%3A%20turmeric%20pods%20weighing%208.