to%20rediscover%20the%20joy%20of%20reading%20and%20exploring%20new%20books.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOm%20and%20Heet%20are%20working%20hard%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20libraries%20remain%20stocked%20with%20books%2C%20and%20they%20rely%20on%20donations%20from%20individuals%20and%20groups%20to%20keep%20the%20libraries%20running%20smoothly.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20never%20charge%20for%20books%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Heet.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20only%20ask%20for%20funds%20to%20help%20with%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20libraries%20and%20people%20donate%20books%20to%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-25-at-11.26.10_11zon-1740544640-500x667.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20mini%20public%20libraries%20are%20free%20for%20all%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-25-at-11.26.10_11zon-1740544640-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-25-at-11.26.10_11zon-1740544640-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-25-at-11.26.10_11zon-1740544640-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-25-at-11.26.10_11zon-1740544640-1152x1536.jpeg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-25-at-11.26.10_11zon-1740544640-900x1200.jpeg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-25-at-11.26.10_11zon-1740544640-600x800.jpeg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-25-at-11.26.10_11zon-1740544640-450x